_sText:
Have you ever wondered where the dev blocks in all the maps come from? Now is your chance to visit an abandoned dev block quarry. But be carefull not to fall down!

This is an older map i've been workin on and thought was broken since it took forever to compile... but managed to get it to work finally. Pretty simple (tier 2) and short (~50 second) map. Theres also a short 30 second kz bonus with no checkpoints.
